HEADWORD: Churrus
<hw>Chur"rus</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind.
<ets>charas</ets>.]</ety> <def>A powerfully narcotic and intoxicating
gum resin which exudes from the flower heads, seeds, etc., of Indian
hemp.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

